# Cloudflare Pages Redirects Configuration
# SPA(Single Page Application) 라우팅 지원

# Redirect all routes to index.html for client-side routing
/*    /index.html   200

# API redirects (if needed in future)
# /api/*  https://your-api-endpoint.com/:splat  200

# Security redirects
# Force HTTPS (Cloudflare handles this automatically, but keeping for reference)
# http://your-domain.com/*  https://your-domain.com/:splat  301!